title: Marvel NOW! Week 51 11/06/2013
description:
Sorry for the delay, folks. Strangely, I (again) didn't see a collected torrent for last this past week's Marvel NOW! titles, so I thought I'd upload one. Included are:

Amazing X-Men 001 (you know what they say about comic book deaths)
Captain America 013
Captain Marvel 017
Daredevil - Dark Nights 006 (of 8) (it's Palmiotti. Read it on principle)
Iron Man 018
Longshot Saves the Marvel Universe 001 (of 4) <-- looking forward to this, myself! Huzzah, Longshot!
Mighty Avengers 003
X-Men Legacy 019

If you like them and have the money, buy them and support your favorite writers, artists, local comic shops and publishers. Thanks be to all you uploaders and scanners and seeders out there! Enjoy, and please do seed :]
